title: Hello I need help form the LoL my game as a issue
body:
bY GAME KEEPPS WONT LET ME OPEN IT WHEN I TRY TO DEBUG IT THIS POPS UP Unhandled exception at 0x73A52F4B (msvcr80.dll) in rads_user_kernel.exe: 0xC0000005: Access violation reading location 0xA35E1A69.

If there is a handler for this exception, the program may be safely continued. IN STUIDO CODE pLZ help me

replies.body:
This type of error is usually caused by a Firewall or Antivirus preventing League from running properly. I recommend *temporarily disabling* any of those programs that may be causing this issue. If you don't know how, you can simply [**perform a clean boot**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting#wq3) to prevent those programs from running.

Let me know if this helped.
